snippet.title: Just Cause 3 Multiplayer - Preview Announcement
snippet.description:
More information on the preview: https://community.nanos.io/index.php?/topic/192-announcing-the-jc3mp-preview/

"nanos JC3:MP" is a multiplayer modification for Just Cause 3 allowing playing on customisable dedicated servers. Be sure to visit our homepage at http://just-cause.mp/

The final version of "nanos JC3:MP" will be released later in 2016.
